# Project-specific overrides only — base ruleset is fetched at format-time from
# brzzdev/Configs (see the `format` recipe in the justfile).

# The base config sets `--header strip`. This project is AGPL-3.0-or-later, so
# every source file instead carries an SPDX identifier: GitHub's detector only
# sees `AGPL-3.0` from the LICENSE file, and "or later" exists only where we
# assert it. `swiftformat --lint` fails on a missing header, so CI enforces it.
--header //\n// Copyright © {created.year} brzzdev\n// SPDX-License-Identifier: AGPL-3.0-or-later\n//
